Database migrations for the clinical intake application.

## Running migrations

    # Apply all pending migrations (safe to run on every deploy)
    alembic upgrade head

    # Check current revision
    alembic current

    # Stamp an existing database (skip running 001 if schema already exists)
    alembic stamp 001

    # Generate a new migration after changing schema.sql
    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe_the_change"

## First deploy on a new machine

    alembic upgrade head

## Existing databases (before Alembic was introduced)

    alembic stamp 001   # mark as already at baseline
    alembic upgrade head  # apply any newer migrations
